ying to university. </p>  </div>  </div> </aside>  </div>  <div data-module="" class="Module StudyPortals_Shared_Modules_article_RelatedArticles_RelatedArticles">  <aside id="RelatedArticlesContainer">  <h3 class="RelatedTitle">Keep reading</h3> <div id="RelatedArticles">  <figure class="RelatedArticle"> <a class="ArticleAnchor" href="https://www.mastersportal.com/articles/1662/times-higher-education-ranking-2021-best-european-universities.html" target="_blank" title="Times Higher Education Ranking 2021 - Best European Universities"> <div class="ArticleImageContainer"> <img class="ArticleImage" src="//storage-prtl-co.imgix.net/endor/articles/1662/images/1521547578_56e7ceea95003.jpg?h=180&amp;w=395&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format&amp;q=40" alt="Times Higher Education Ranking 2021 - Best European Universities" loading="lazy" width="263" height="180"> </div> <div class="ArticleName"> <span class="ArticleNameHolder">Times Higher Education Ranking 2021 - Best European Universities</span> </div> </a> </figure>  <figure class="RelatedArticle"> <a class="ArticleAnchor" href="https://www.mastersportal.com/articles/2023/5-reasons-why-university-rankings-are-not-perfect.html" target="_blank" title="5 Reasons Why University Rankings Are Not Perfect"> <div class="ArticleImageContainer"> <img class="ArticleImage" src="//storage-prtl-co.imgix.net/endor/articles/2023/images/1541672814_steven-lelham-342930-unsplash.jpg?h=180&amp;w=395&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format&amp;q=40" alt="5 Reasons Why University Rankings Are Not Perfect" loading="lazy" width="263" height="180"> </div> <div class="ArticleName"> <span class="ArticleNameHolder">5 Reasons Why University Rankings Are Not Perfect</span> </div> </a> </figure>  </div>  </aside>  </div>  <div data-module="SPScholarships" class="Module StudyPortals_Shared_Modules_SPScholarships_SPScholarships StudyPortals_Shared_Modules_SPScholarships_SPScholarshipsArticle"> <aside id="SPScholarships"> <div class="ContentCard